results.title: Lost and Found
results.description: The X-Men and Acolytes crash land on earth and try to regroup; Callisto finds Colossus and asks for his help in saving the world.

results.title: The Enemy of My Enemy...
results.description: Rogue and Iceman are on a road trip trying to deal with the things Rogue absorbed from Gambit when she kissed him; Gambit shows up and Rogue decides to leave him and the X-Men for awhile; The connection between Remey and Mr. Sinister is revealed.

results.title: The Totally Unexpected Return of the X-Babies !
They're Back...
results.description: Gambit and Bishop are out for a night on the town when they run across the X-Babies running for their lives from Gog and Magog.

results.title: Big Trouble In Little Italy !
results.description: The X-Men try to rescue the X-Babies from Gag and Magog; The X-Babies return to Mojoworld to live with Dazzler and Longshot; Xavier comes to a decision about Sabretooth.

results.title: Five Card Studs
results.description: The X-Men enjoy a friendly game of poker; Bishop tries to come to terms with visions of his future self; Sugar Man and Dark Beast hook up and decide to take down Bishop as he is the only one who remembers the Age of Apocalypse.

results.title: It's an All-Out Battle When...Bishop Goes Wild !
Eyes of a New York Woman
results.description: Dark Beast sends Fatale after Bishop before he realizes that he can prey on the X-Men better by targeting his double, a certain fuzzy Dr. Hank McCoy.

results.title: Blowback
results.description: Wolverine is captured by Omega Red and Fenris so they can probe his memories to find a Carbonadium Synthesizer that has been lost for 30 years; Wolvie escapes with the help of an old friend; The X-Men come after him as well.

results.title: Full Court Press
results.description: Four X-Men are transported to another dimension where they are confronted by Onslaught's herald, Post, who tests them in battle for his master's benefit.

results.title: Deathbound Train
results.description: A strong spike in Cerebro sends the X-Men to a commuter train filled with humans mutated into monsters by Mr. Sinister.

results.title: Collector's Item
results.description: Mr. Sinister captures Bishop and begins delving into his past (or was that future); Dark Beast gets Gambit to interrupt the experiment before Sinister taps Bish's memory of the Age of Apocalypse and discovers that the Hank he has in custody isn't the real McCoy.

results.title: False Fronts
results.description: Onslaught pulls Jean into the astral plane and casts aspersions on Xavier's character and his dream; Jean refuses to join him (of course) which makes the mysterious villain in Magneto like costume very mad indeed.

items.name: X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Vol. 1 TPB (2007)
X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Vol. 1 TPB (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Inquiring Minds
results.description: Juggernaut shows up at the mansion so Jean can remove a mental block and help him discover who Onslaught is; Beast escapes from Dark Beast's prison; Onslaught captures Juggernaut and rips the Gem of Cyttorak from his body; Xavier is revealed as Onslaught.

items.name: X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Vol. 1 TPB (2007)
X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Vol. 1 TPB (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Onslaught Phase 1: Twilight of the Heroes
Invasion
results.description: The X-Men, Avengers and FF vainly try to thwart Onslaught and his Sentinels from plans of world conquest.

items.name: X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Book 3 (2008)
X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Book 3 (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Onslaught Phase 2: Magneto and Rogue Unleashed !
The Beginning of the End: Twilight of the Gods
results.description: Rogue and Joseph fight for their lives against Sentinels; Onslaught tries to siphon off X-Man's power; The heroes try to figure out how to beat their awesomely powerful foe; Xavier confronts Onslaught.

items.name: X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Book 4 (2008 - Present)
X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Book 4 (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Man
results.description: Beast reunites with Trish; Bastion pays J.J. Jameson a visit; Val shows up to arrest a powerless Xavier for his part in the Onslaught affair, and Professor X agrees to be taken into custody.

items.name: X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Book 4 (2008 - Present)
X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Book 4 (Trade Paperback)

results.title: It Had to Happen--Gambit vs. Magneto !
Testament
results.description: Gambit and Joseph tussle over a misunderstanding about Rogue.

results.title: Touched
results.description: Hercules shows up at X-Mansion to reunite with his old Avengers buddy Quicksilver; Scott and Jean go to the movies.

results.title: Farther Still
results.description: Maverick tries to help Wolvie heal up; Psylocke is taken over by Matsuo and helps Sabretooth capture the X-Men; Psylock and Sabretooth then go after and capture Maverick and Logan.

results.title: Night
results.description: Candra comes after Storm as a gem that she stole as a child contains the Immortal's soul; Jamil, possessed by the Shadow King, obtains the gem; Jean and Sam talk about the death of Graydon Creed.

results.title: Bolt
results.description: Storm and the X-Men try to keep Candra from reclaiming the source of her powers.

results.title: Games of Deceit & Death Part 1
results.description: The X-Men meet up with Shang-Chi and travel to Hong Kong to see if Fu Manchu's "elixir vitae" may hold a cure to the Legacy Virus.

results.title: Games of Deceit & Death Part 2
results.description: The X-Men, the Black King and the Kingpin of Crime all vie for possession of the elixir vitae.

results.title: Must An X-Man Die...To Cure the Legacy Virus?!
Games of Deceit & Death Part 3
results.description: The battle for the elixir vitae concludes with the possible cure for the Legacy Virus being destroyed; Shang-Chi decides to return to the life of a hero; On the way back to the states, the X-Men are accosted by Operation Zero Tolerance.

results.title: Operation: Zero Tolerance Prologue: First Blood
results.description: The Prime Sentinels of Zero Tolerance make short work of the X-Men; Bastion invades X-Mansion and taunts Xavier with the knowledge that he will crack the Shi'ar language giving him access to all of the Professor's information on mutants.

results.title: Because You Demanded It--The Return of Iceman !
Start Spreadin' The News...
results.description: Iceman comes to the aid of an E.R. doctor who has been targeted by the Prime Sentinels for her mutant abilities.

results.title: The End of Days
results.description: Sabra is targeted by the Prime Sentinels but escapes; Iceman and Cecilia have their own Sentinel problems as they are betrayed by Bobby's old pal, Charlotte Jones.

results.title: Heart of the Matter
results.description: Marrow and Charlotte help Bobby and Cecilia escape from the Prime Sentinels; Senator Kelly begins to rethink his support of Zero Tolerance.

results.title: Last Exit
results.description: Iceman and crew have a final showdown with Bastion before SHIELD comes in and shuts Operation Zero Tolerance down.

results.title: Inside...Out!
results.description: Psylocke breaks Matsuo's conditioning and helps Maverick facilitate the X-Men's escape.

results.title: Homecoming
results.description: The X-Men return from their fight with Bastion to find X-Mansion completely stripped of everything but the bare walls by Zero Tolerance; Scott has a nano-bomb in his chest and the X-Folk, old and new, have to pull together to save his life; In the midst of the operation, Juggernaut comes calling to lay claim to his half-brother's assets and decides to beat on his foes in a moment of weakness.

results.title: When Cyclops and Phoenix Leave--Will the Dream Survive?
A House In Order
results.description: The new X-Men try to fit into their new lives; Scott and Jean leave so that Cyke can recover from his injuries at the hands of Bastion; The heroes return from Heroes Reborn; Wolvie is left in charge of the mansion.

results.title: Life Lessons
results.description: Wolverine tries to help Marrow fit into the X-Men and ends up in a life and death struggle with the former Morlock; Magneto returns with Sabra and Gabrielle on his trail.

results.title: The Elements Within Us
results.description: The X-Men make New Years Resolutions; Sabra shows up to kill Joseph thinking he is Magneto, but the two end up leaving to find the real Master of Magnetism.

results.title: Rituals
results.description: Marrow saves Archangel from Abomination in the Morlock tunnels; Wolvie investigates murders in Salem Center that point to Maggott's slugs.

results.title: Anatomy of a Monster
results.description: The X-Men's inquiry into who assaulted (and autopsied) Wolverine leads to a N'Garai cairn and another race of earth conquering alien demons.

results.title: A Boykie and His Dinges
results.description: Maggott tells Wolvie his strange origin and how Magneto saved his life and helped him understand his mutant powers.

results.title: Psi-War Part 1: Wolverine and Psylocke Against a Legion !
Stormfront
results.description: Storm and the X-Men travel to Kenya to aid her old mentor, Ainet; The Shadow King pulls the X-Folk into the astral plane for a battle royale; During a battle between the Shadow King and Psylocke, all psi-powers on earth become dampened.

results.title: Psi-War Part 2: With the World's Fate in Her Hands--Could This Be Psylocke's Last Stand?
Stormfront Part 2
results.description: Psylocke and the Shadow King duke it out on the astral plane; Psylocke wins by containing the Shadow King within herself but loses her psychic abilities in the process.

results.title: Little Morlock Lost
results.description: Marrow goes on a tear through New York when she learns that Sam may be returning home to Kentucky to care for his sick mother; Storm and Callisto help Sam track her down and convince her to give life with the X-Men a real shot.

results.title: Tooth and Claw
results.description: Bishop has it out with Gambit; The X-Men enjoy a nice afternoon picnic when Gambit's wife shows up to crash the party.

results.title: Children of the Atom
results.description: The X-Men reform to take on a band of fake X-Folk who are being led by a cold and calculating Xavier.

results.title: A Vision of Things to Come...
Rogue and Gambit Reunited--But Will It Be In Death?
Jack of Hearts, Queen of Death
results.description: Gambit tries to reintegrate himself into the X-Men; Once Rogue and Gambit find some time to themselves, Kali shows up to break up the reunion.

results.title: The Hunt For Xavier Part 2: What Is The Secret of the Two Xaviers?
The Hunt for Xavier Part Two: The Hunt for Charley !
results.description: The X-Men are in Siberia trying to locate Xavier and are sent on a mind trip by a little girl trying to protect Cerebro.

results.title: The Hunt for Xavier Part 4: Cerebro Ascendant
The Hunt for Xavier Part Four: Tomb of Ice
results.description: The X-Men try to fight off Cerebro but fail; Cerebro takes over Colossus' body and beats the Russian's teammates to a pulp; Cerebro collects Nina and heads for Alcatraz.

results.title: The Hunt for Xavier: The Conclusion
The Hunt for Xavier The Conclusion: Dream's End !
results.description: Xavier and the X-Men beat Cerebro at its own game and end the threat to mutants everywhere.

results.title: A Tale of Two Mutants
results.description: The X-Men save a nursery full of babies in a burning hospital; Magneto gives an average human an unfair test to see if humanity is fit to exist or if he should launch his Magneto War.

results.title: Thanks for the Memories
results.description: Astra tells Joseph his full origin and how she created him using Magneto as a template; The X-Men take on the Acolytes; Magneto holds the world in abject terror of his power so they try to nuke him.

results.title: No Surrender !
results.description: The X-Men take the fight to Magneto; Joseph sacrifices himself to save the world from being destroyed; The U.N. gives Maggie sole rulership of Genosha in return for his agreement never to launch another attack against humanity.
